Package tagalong.units

Enum Class AccelerationUnits

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<AccelerationUnits>
tagalong.units.AccelerationUnits
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<AccelerationUnits>, Constable
public enum AccelerationUnits extends Enum<AccelerationUnits>
Acceleration units enum identifiers. Used for configuration and robot setup instead of the WPILib Java units to avoid reallocations and garbage collections in match.
